CMT has been established for nearly 40 years, we’ve always importing the most advanced equipments and materials, on the other hand, we also expands our supply of key materials from the following industries: TFT-LCD, semiconductor, telecommunication materials / chemicals, solar energy, and environmental friendly products, to best serve our customers and suppliers, CMT is looking forward to work closely and grow together with our customers and suppliers.

