關鍵字(中)
金融控股公司金控集團共同行銷


關鍵字(英)
Cross-sellingFinancial Holding CompanyFinancial Holding Group (Financial Holding Compa


學科別分類



中文摘要
金融控股公司法公佈後，提供了一個金控集團進行共同行銷的法制基礎，本文乃針對實際具體之共同行銷行為加以類型化，並分別分析其法律適用，以探討相關管制規範之回應。參考金融控股公司法第43條規定，以及金融控股公司及其子公司自律規範第2條關於共同行銷之定義，本文將金控集團之共同行銷行為區分為共同業務推廣行為、資訊交互運用行為、共用營業場所、設備、人員以及販售組合型金融商品等四種行為。大體而言，本文論述的重點在於共同行銷、共同行銷與競爭法制、共同行銷與消費者保護，所以，對於相關金融政策、金融行銷在法制上的特殊性、金融控股公司本身在集團內的角色扮演、競爭法制對於各類共同行銷行為的管制等重要問題，透過檢視我國各項法規、整理主管機關所發佈的見解以及參考外國立法例，本文均分別提出具體主張，希望能釐清實務適用法規時之相關疑義，並能作為將來修法時之參考。  


英文摘要
Following the promulgation of the Financial Holding Company Act provided a legal standard for cross-selling activities of Financial Holding Group (Financial Holding Company and its Subsidiary(ies)). This paper is on Legal Norm of Cross-selling of the Financial Holding Group, providing the classification of actual cross-selling activities, analysis on application of law and discussion about repercussion of relevant rules and regulations. The cross-selling activities of the Financial Holding Group is hereby, refer to the definition as used in Article 43 of the Financial Holding Company Act and Article 2 of the Self-disciplinary Rules Governing the Activities of the Financial Holding Company, classified into four kinds of activities including cross-selling, sharing of information, sharing of business facilities and premises, and the sale of combined financial products. Emphasis, given to in this paper, include cross-selling, cross-selling and regulations of competition, cross-selling and the protection of consumers’ rights and interests. By canvassing various rules and laws and by marshaling interpretations and explanations issued by the competent authority and referring to Acts of other countries, concrete advices given and cited hereby in this paper, regarding relevant financial policy, the special of financial selling in the legal system, the role and position of Financial Holding Company itself in the Financial Holding Group, and the Fair Trade Act and any relevant laws and regulations governing various cross-selling activities, in order to clarify misunderstandings and mistakes incurred in application of law and to be as reference to the amendment of relevant laws.  


論文目次
