學科別分類



中文摘要
隨著全球化趨勢的蔓延、消費者意識高漲以及環境保護觀念的興起，使企業除了要面對環保團體的抗爭和法令的限制，國際貿易製裁及環保公約也間接成為企業經營壓力的來源。2008年金融海嘯襲捲全球，不僅使多家重量級金融機構倒閉，企業為節流更吹起裁員風，失業勞工為爭取工作權忿而向資方怒吼，勞資間存在已久的矛盾與衝突一觸即發，企業面臨要選擇求公司生存或維繫員工生計的兩難局面，勞資雙方的不信任感在短時間內可能難以輓回，企業如何才能符合社會期待並永續經營，已成為企業刻不容緩的重要議題！聯合國《二十一世紀議程》與台灣所制定的《二十一世紀議程－中華民國永續發展策略綱領》中，都強調企業永續發展的重要性，企業為追求永續發展的理想，運用永續性評比工具來評估自身永續績效將是未來的趨勢，在國內企業多年努力下，如今台灣在國際供應鏈中扮演舉足輕重角色情況下，國內企業必須對國際間企業永續發展的意涵與作法做更深入的瞭解。因此本研究將以個案研究與文獻蒐集的方式，探討目前國內兩家已列名DJSI之標竿企業如何致力於企業社會責、如何積極投入社會責任投資進行分析討論，並藉由標竿企業社會責任投資模式的學習，期望建構一套嚴謹且適用於國內企業參考的企業社會責任評量系統，更希望透過永續績效評比工具的運用，讓國內企業開始重視其永續績效。


英文摘要
With the spread of globalization, consumer awareness is high, as well as the emergence of the concept of environmental protection, enterprises have to face the environmental groups in addition to the protest of the restrictions and regulations, international trade sanctions and environmental conventions have also indirectly become the source of pressure on the operation of enterprise. In 2008, the global financial tsunami, not only the closure of a number of heavyweight financial institutions, enterprises more blow for the expenditure to lay off workers, unemployed workers strive for the right to work for the roar of anger to the management, one slight touch and off it goes imminently between employers and employees have been in existence for a long time the explosive contradictions and conflicts, enterprises are facing for dilemma that the company to choose to survive or maintain their employees livelihood, a sense of trust between the two sides ,employers and employees, may be difficult to recover in a short period of time, how can we meet the society expectations and long-term viability of enterprises has become an important issue for enterprises without delay.  United Nations< 21 century agenda> and Taiwan set< 21 century agenda - sustainable development strategic outlines in the Republic of China> stressed the importance of sustainable development enterprises, enterprises in pursuit of the ideals of sustainable development, the use of sustainability evaluation tools to assess the self-sustainable performance will be future trend; in the efforts of domestic enterprises for many years, now,in the circumstances, Taiwan play an important role at the international supply chain. At the same time, domestic enterprises must be doing a more in-depth understanding for the implications and the practice of international enterprise of sustainable development. Therefore, this study will be the way to collect case studies and literatures to explore two current members are listed on the benchmark DJSI, how to commit to corporate social responsibility, how to participate actively in to discuss the society responsibility of investment analysis, and by benchmarking corporate social investment model of study, it expects to build a set of strict construction, applicable to domestic enterprises, and the information to assess corporate social responsibility system, but also hope that, through sustainable use of performance appraisal tools, domestic enterprises started to attach importance to its sustainable performance.


